OL,3,CAirports confirm nationwide border
OL,4,Cissue as e-gate problems cause delays
OL,6,FThe Home Office has confirmed airports
OL,7,Facross the country are being impacted
OL,8,Fby problems with UK Border Force e-
OL,9,Fgates
OL,11,Fare facing severe delays across the UK
OL,12,Fas airports confirm a nationwide issue
OL,13,Fto border services.
OL,15,FHeathrow, Stanstead, Manchester,
OL,16,FGatwick and Glasgow airports airports
OL,17,Fhave all confirmed they are impacted
OL,18,Fby problems with UK Border Force e-
OL,19,Fgates.
