OL,3,CAirports confirm nationwide border
OL,4,Cissue as e-gate problems cause delays
OL,6,FImages and footage shared on social
OL,7,Fmedia on Tuesday evening appeared to
OL,8,Fshow long queues forming at the gates,
OL,9,Fwhich scan passports.
OL,11,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,12,Fare aware of a technical issue
OL,13,Faffecting e-gates across the country.
OL,15,F"We are working closely with Border
OL,16,FForce and affected airports to resolve
OL,17,Fthe issue as soon as possible and
OL,18,Fapologise to all passengers for the
OL,19,Finconvenience caused."
