OL,6,FNathan Lane, a passenger stuck in
OL,7,FHeathrow, told ITV News: "They really
OL,8,Fseemed to be having a meltdown. It
OL,9,Fseemed to be happening right when we
OL,10,Flanded. Staff were yelling and all the
OL,11,Fe-gates were down - so immediately it
OL,12,Fwas clear something bad was happening.
OL,14,F"It took me about two hours I'd say,
OL,15,Fand we were towards the front. I can't
OL,16,Feven imagine for the people who kept
OL,17,Fbeing added to the back of the queue."
