OL,4,Cissue as e-gate problems cause delays
OL,6,FKevin Wood, who was stuck in
OL,7,FStanstead, told ITV News: "I believe
OL,8,Fthat there has been a nationwide IT
OL,9,Ffailure at Border Force.
OL,11,F"At Stanstead Airport I was sent back
OL,12,Ffrom e-passport machines to join the
OL,13,Fqueue for manual checks then queue
OL,14,Fstopped and we weren't moving as more
OL,15,Fand more people joined.
OL,17,F"We were patronised with repeated
OL,18,Fapology announcements regarding the
OL,19,Ffailure. After an age (about an hour)
OL,20,Fwe started moving as they slowly
OL,21,Fpopulated the booths."
