OL,12,Fwith their contingency plans to help
OL,13,Fresolve the problem as quickly as
OL,14,Fpossible and we apologise for any
OL,15,Fimpact."
OL,17,FA Manchester Airport spokesperson
OL,18,Fsaid: "We are aware of an issue with
OL,19,FUK Border Force's systems across the
OL,20,Fcountry, affecting a significant
OL,21,Fnumber of airports.
